    <div class="row mt-4">
      <div class="col-lg-12" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="additional-info">
          <h3>Why Choose EngrHire BD?</h3>
          <p>
            EngrHire BD stands out as the go-to platform for construction professionals and clients due to its commitment to innovation, transparency, and excellence. Here's why you should choose us:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"></i> Diverse Pool of Experts</li>
            <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"></i> Secure and Confidential Transactions</li>
            <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"></i> User-Friendly Interface</li>
            <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"></i> Real-time Collaboration Tools</li>
